{"tid":997561,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"RTX2060完勝GTX1070，GTX1070仲好意思賣3000","createTime":"2019-01-27T09:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T10:07:28.000Z","uid":175335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"06fa78b13186abea24b2a24301ebefd915514a80","tid":997561,"uid":175335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"上周，NVIDIA 最新型號 GeForce RTX 2060 正式賣街，開價低至 $2,850，成為 RTX 20 系列入場費最低之型號，即時對各款舊有型號帶來極大衝擊，GTX 1060 與 GTX 1070 雙雙創新低價，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=18cddc71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 直擊顯示卡最新戰況。<br />\n<br />\n最平 $2,850 有交易<br />\n<br />\n各牌子 RTX 2060 大軍殺到，包括：ASUS、GALAX、GIGABYTE、Inno3D、MSI、ZOATAC 等牌子。RTX 2060 Founders Edition 官方定價為 US$349 (約 HK$2,722)，雖然香港沒有 FE 版售賣，但不少牌子之首發型號，開價皆不到 $3,000。當中最便宜的是 ZOTAC Twin Fan，開價 $2,850 平盡全場；GIGABYTE OC 型號亦不到 $2,900。此外，GALAX、Inno3D TWIN X2、ZOTAC AMP 等型號，售價均在 $3,000 以下。至於全場最貴之 RTX 2060，要數到 ASUS STRIX A Gaming 與 STRIX Gaming 兩兄弟，分別叫價 $3,399 及 $3,499，比最平價一款 RTX 2060 貴超過 $500。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/GTX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2FGTX&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=97c0ef7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/GTX</a> 1060 6GB 跌破 $1,800<br />\n<br />\nRTX 2060 登陸 $3,000 價位市場，上代相近價位之 GTX 10 系列早已開始劈價清貨，當中 GTX 1070 重回 $3,000 內，全場最平的 Leadtek 更劈至 $2,500 有找。部分昔日貴價型號如：GIGABYTE G1 Gaming、Inno3D iChill X3 等，最新市價亦回落到 $3,000 以下。GTX 1060 6GB 版本一直企硬於 $2,000 水平，上周終於大幅降價，由 Palit Dual 帶頭創下 $1,799 新低價，其他牌子暫未跟隨，依然叫價近 $2,000。AMD 陣營方面，Radeon RX 580 8GB 早前劈穿 $1,900，最近 HIS IceQ X OC 劈上劈，率先降至 $1,600 有找，比死對頭 GTX 1060 6GB 再平 $200，甚至比 GTX 1060 3GB 便宜。"},{"pid":"b64242939b1d26b165467398acac9be125594623","tid":997561,"uid":79829,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:27:44.000Z","msg":"有d人好介意得6gb ram<br />\n1070 有8gb"},{"pid":"f83c838c8467d99e2d58f515178aad9e88b613f1","tid":997561,"uid":133927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:12:30.000Z","msg":"講到咁好你咪去買囉, 1070減唔減又關你事既?"},{"pid":"0666e33d9c388023f40837640497c61c78279186","tid":997561,"uid":1886,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"f83c838c8467d99e2d58f515178aad9e88b613f1","tid":997561,"uid":133927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:12:30.000Z","msg":"講到咁好你咪去買囉, 1070減唔減又關你事既?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"好多新聞時事同其他報道都未必唔關你事，洗唔洗逐個 post 入去屌？<br />\n<br />\n討論區原意係乜搞清楚未？？"},{"pid":"bcb9c175e896bca02179a1e581c00e81b97c80e3","tid":997561,"uid":24412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"2060好似係暫時性價比最高既卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9478094f6d5c7aae3659a8c2ccb272574aa5fe7","tid":997561,"uid":77771,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcb9c175e896bca02179a1e581c00e81b97c80e3","tid":997561,"uid":24412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"2060好似係暫時性價比最高既卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqMPxuT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqMPxuT.png&h=c83c4c1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28f9f41c53a4f43b2054af190290d4ae3ffe5639","tid":997561,"uid":82301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"8gb vs 6gb<br />\n有貨vs冇貨"},{"pid":"21b0fe031d3b3f8d3f3231b533a60dba48fa9211","tid":997561,"uid":36136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:51:35.000Z","msg":"咪等1070大跌囉"},{"pid":"8f1869867a23d458fc28726e967ad0635b89de2d","tid":997561,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl